{"comments":"Core type definitions for NURBS (Non-Uniform Rational B-Splines).\n\n## Overview\n\nThis module defines the fundamental types for NURBS curve representation:\n- ControlPoint: Weighted control point with position and weight\n- KnotVector: Non-decreasing sequence of parameter values\n- NurbsCurve: Complete NURBS curve with control points, knots, and degree\n\n## Mathematical Foundation\n\nA NURBS curve of degree p is defined as:\n\n```\nC(u) = Σᵢ (Nᵢ,ₚ(u) · wᵢ · Pᵢ) / Σᵢ (Nᵢ,ₚ(u) · wᵢ)\n```\n\nWhere:\n- Pᵢ are control points\n- wᵢ are weights (positive numbers)\n- Nᵢ,ₚ(u) are B-spline basis functions of degree p\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Hydrogen.Schema.Geometry.Point (Point2D for positions)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["position",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Point"],"Point2D"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["weight",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[75,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Nurbs/Types.purs","start":[72,22]},"title":"ControlPoint"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Geometry","Nurbs","Types"],"ControlPoint"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[77,50],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Geometry/Nurbs/Types.purs","start":[77,1]},"title":"eqControlPoint"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"t